data.description: NEW IMPACT WINDOWS HAVE BEEN INSTALLED!!  Welcome to this gorgeous, move in ready home in Port Charlotte, Florida!  Close to shopping, dining and fun family activities and less than 15 minutes to the NEW Sunseeker resort and a quick drive over the Charlotte Harbor bridge to Downtown Punta Gorda! This home has over 2,000sqft with 3 bedrooms and 2 large bathrooms! A large family room greets you as you enter this well maintained home with natural sunlight and a refreshing breeze thanks to the large windows and slider doors. Dining room is right off the kitchen and just a step up from the living room! Your new kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and passthrough windows for bright natural sunlight and access to the lanai for great entertainment! Another family room is just off the kitchen and it is currently being used as a formal dining area and sitting area with another door off to the lanai! Primary bedroom features NEW vinyl plank flooring and a slider off to the lanai! A spacious en suite bathroom, walk-in closet and linen closet reside this master suite! Bedroom 2 features NEW vinyl plank flooring and a large walk-in closet! Bedroom 3 is currently being used as an office and does not have a closet, however, there is plenty of room to add one! Bathroom 2 features a large vanity and large linen closet and even has a door accessing the lanai for your future pool! Now welcome to your new outdoor entertainment space! Newly screened in lanai and very spacious area to host friends and family! Roof is new 2021. AC is 2017 and serviced every 6 months. Newer electrical panel and water heater. Welcome home!
